    'guida.tip2.h': 'Save snapshots often',
    'guida.tip2.p': 'Before any major editing operation, save a snapshot. It takes 2 seconds and protects against accidental loss of work.',
    'guida.tip3.h': 'Slim down large EPUBs',
    'guida.tip3.p': 'If an EPUB has too many images, use ePub Slimmer before importing. Significantly reduces loading time and IndexedDB space.',
